images.alt:
📢 New themes start every Sunday night!
Up next: #AiTheme2025Week35 – “Scenes You Haven’t Seen” 🎬✨
The unseen, the overlooked, the in-between—discover the parts of the story left out.

I’ve been keeping a little “idea box” for future weeks, and I’d love to hear what sparks your imagination. 

Here’s a loose list of possible themes (in no particular order):

* In Motion – Travel, liminal spaces, shifting worlds
* Dream Logic – Surreal rules and strange connections
* Elemental Forces – Raw power, nature, and primal spirits
* Lost & Found – Forgotten, rediscovered, or imagined anew
* Video Games – Inspired by games, styles, or aesthetics
* Overgrown – Nature reclaiming spaces, beautiful decay
* Patch Notes – Absurd or playful character/world updates
* Sweet & Sticky – Cute, chaotic, or tempting in sugary form
* Living Architecture – Cities that grow, and homes that breathe
* Whispering Shadows – Mysterious figures and secrets in the dark
* Velvet Touch – Sensual textures and tactile experiences
* Moonlit Serenade – Romantic and mysterious nighttime encounters
* Critter Companion – Who’s your little friend?
* Glow Up – Makeup, illumination, or bioluminescence
* Unexpected Accessory – A jeweled eyepatch? A cheese purse?
* Cozy Corners – Warm light, hidden nooks, and peaceful spaces

Which one would you love to see next? Or suggest something brand new—I’m always open to more ideas. 💡
